The paper deals with face recognition and security, which are topics related to computer vision (cs.CV) and cryptography and security (cs.CR). The use of Deep Neural Networks also suggests that the paper could belong to machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. Finally, the mention of cross-database testing and pre-training on large face recognition datasets suggests that the paper could also belong to information retrieval (cs.IR).
